Title: 1 vs 100
Description:
This is a project based on the popular game show 1 vs 100.  This project will use C# and utilize WPF as the GUI and 3.5 .NET framework.  Developed to learn more about WPF
*All images and music used is not used in any commercial way, strictly used for enhancing learning experience
